FireResist 5

Napalm breath (Su)
1 Standard action
10-ft. cone, 2d6 fire plus Clinging Flames, Reflex DC 10+1/2lvl+ConMod for half
Usable every 1d4 rounds
Clinging Flames:
  If damaged by Napalm Breath, subject is Burning.  No save.
  1d6 damage for 1d4 rounds, Full-round Reflex save to extinguish

